DEFAULT - In this mode, objects parent directly to the player. CPU expensive, but most accurate. Objects can clip into environment sometimes tho.=默认-在此模式下，物体直接与玩家关联。耗费CPU性能，但最准确。但物体有时可以卡进环境中。
In this mode, objects float freely in world, are MUCH cheaper on CPU, but drifts badly with smooth locomotion. Use only if making guns with TONS of attachments.=在此模式下，物体在世界中自由漂浮，占用CPU性能更少，但平滑移动时漂移严重。仅用于制作带有大量配件的枪支。

Designed For Oculus-Style Controllers\n- -\nFirearms use Trigger, A & B buttons\nAnalog Sticks are used ONLY for movement\nThis mode is closest to 'Standard' VR Game controls\n- -\nBest option for Twinstick style locomotion\nStrongly Recommended for all controllers except Vive Wands and Gen 1 WMR Controllers.=专为Oculus风格控制器设计\n- -\n枪支使用扳机、A和B按钮\n摇杆仅用于移动\n此模式最接近“标准”VR游戏控制\n- -\n双摇杆风格移动的最佳选择\n强烈推荐用于除Vive Wands和第一代WMR控制器之外的所有控制器。
Originally Designed For Vive Wands\n- -\nFirearms use Trigger, 2Axis Input\nMovement uses Menu / B Button\nHas full complex control set of all weapon types\n--\nNot recommended for controllers that only have a single 2Axis input (touchpad OR joystick but not both) UNLESS you're using Teleport/Dash or Armswinger Movement=最初为Vive Wands设计\n- -\n枪械使用扳机，2轴输入\n使用菜单或B按钮移动\n拥有所有武器类型的完整复杂控制集\n--\n不推荐用于仅有单个2轴输入的控制器（触摸板或操纵杆，但不能同时使用），除非你使用传送/冲刺或摆臂移动方式

2. When in A Sandbox Scene, use an ITEM SPAWNER to spawn objects.\n--\nYou can duplicate mags, ammo and grenades by putting them in your Quickbelt and clicking your Touchpad/Joystick or A (based on Control mode)=2. 在沙盒场景中，使用物品生成器生成物体。\n--\n你可以将弹匣、弹药和手榴弹放入你的快捷腰带并单击触摸板/摇杆或A（基于你的控制模式）来复制它们
Vive/Rift: Click Menu/B/Y Button to activate locomotion on a hand. Primary 2axis inputs behave like a gamepad (and cannot use weapon functions while active). \n\nIndex/WMR: Joysticks behave like gamepad.\n\nNOTE: There is NO smooth turning available.\n\nGravity & Wall Collision are Enabled.=Vive/Rift：单击菜单/B/Y按钮激活这支手的移动控制。主要2轴输入的行为类似于游戏手柄（并且在激活时无法使用武器功能）。\n\nIndex/WMR：摇杆的行为类似于游戏手柄。\n\n注意：无法使用平滑转向。\n\n重力和墙壁碰撞已启用。
Click Menu/B/Y Button to activate locomotion on a hand. This hand now moves you (and cannot use weapon functions while active).\n\nPress primary 2axis input (touchpad/joystick) forward/up and hold.\n\nDrag input to the side to make arrow at end of arc turn. Release input to teleport.\n\nGravity & Wall Collision are Disabled=单击菜单/B/Y按钮激活这支手的移动控制。这只手现在会移动你（而且激活时无法使用武器功能）。\n\n向前/向上按下主要2轴输入（触摸板/操纵杆）并按住。\n\n将输入拖到一侧可使弧线末端的箭头转动。释放输入即可传送。\n\n重力和墙壁碰撞已禁用
Click-Hold Menu/B/Y Buttons while swinging that controller (in any direction) to increase speed.\n\nThe direction your controller is pointed controls which way you go. If you hold both controller buttons the direction is averaged. \n\nPunching both hands upward while holding buttons is jump!\n\nGravity & Wall Collision are Disabled=按住菜单/B/Y按钮并摆动控制器（朝任意方向）可提高速度。\n\n控制器指向的方向控制着你的前进方向。如果你同时按住两个控制器按钮，则方向会取平均。\n\n按住按钮的同时双手向上挥动就能跳跃！\n\n重力和墙壁碰撞已禁用
Click Menu/B/Y Button to activate locomotion on a hand. This hand now moves you (and cannot use weapon functions while active).\n\nUse primary 2-axis input (touchpad/joystick) to move smoothly\n\nGravity & Wall Collision are Enabled=点击菜单/B/Y按钮激活这支手的移动控制。这只手现在可移动你（激活时无法使用武器功能）。\n\n使用主要2轴输入（触摸板/操纵杆）平滑移动\n\n重力和墙壁碰撞已启用

Greetings!\n\nIf you're new to H3, click through the entries on the left there to get a quick start on things, or click a section on the top bar to spawn some toys to play with!\n\nIf you need help with something there are several helpful links to the left, clicking on them will copy the url to your clip board, which you can paste into a web browser to find more info, or join one of our helpful communities!\n\nAll of us here at RUST LTD. hope you have a Wonderful time!=欢迎！\n\n如果你是H3新手，请点击左侧的条目快速上手，或点击顶栏上的一个部分来生成一些玩具来玩！\n\n如果你需要帮助，左侧有几个有用的链接，点击它们会将URL复制到你的剪贴板，你可以将其粘贴到浏览器中以查找更多信息，或者加入我们的乐于助人的社区之一！\n\nRUST LTD的全体同仁希望你度过愉快的时光！

3x=3x
Click on Top Bar buttons to go to their various pages.\r\n\nEach page will save your selection and tags until you load into a different scene or reload the current scene.\r\n\nThis Spawner is still under construction so some pages may be incomplete or missing.\r=单击顶部栏按钮可转到其各个页面。\r\n\n每个页面都会保存你的选择和标签，直到你加载到不同的场景或重新加载当前场景。\r\n\n此生成器仍在建设中，因此某些页面可能不完整或缺失。\r
Click on the FIREARMS button on the Top Bar.\r\n\nUse the Tag categories section on the left to narrow things down.\r\n\nClick on Gun icons to select them, then, in the right most panel, click the SPAWN button and your gun will appear.\r\n=点击顶部栏上的“枪支”按钮。\r\n\n使用左侧的标签类别部分缩小范围。\r\n\n点击枪支图标进行选择，然后在最右侧面板中点击“生成”按钮，你的枪支就会出现。\r\n
You can Click the SPAWN AMMO PANEL button right on this page.\n\nYou can also click on the AMMO button on the Top Bar to see all Ammo, Magazines, Speedloaders and Stripper Clips available in game.\r\n\nThe Ammo page uses similar Tag sorting to Firearms.\r\r=你可以单击此页面上的“生成弹药面板”按钮。\n\n你还可以单击顶部栏上的“弹药”按钮查看游戏中所有可用的弹药、弹匣、快速装弹器和弹夹。\r\n\n弹药页面使用与枪支类似的标签排序。\r\r
You can SPAWNLOCK ammo, magazines, speedloaders, and clips.\r\n1. Place the object in one of your Quickbelt slots.\r\n2. Hover your empty hand over the slot.\r\n3. Click the B button, the slot will turn blue.\r\n4. You can now take copies of that object out of the slot.\r\n5. Check the HELP section for more detailed Spawnlocking mechanics.\r\n=你可以生成锁定弹药、弹匣、快速装弹器和弹夹。\r\n1. 将物体放入你的快捷腰带插槽之一。\r\n2. 将空手悬停在插槽上。\r\n3. 单击B按钮，插槽将变为蓝色。\r\n4. 你现在可以从插槽中复制该物体。\r\n5. 查看帮助部分以获取更详细的生成锁定机制。\r\n
Pretty much all guns shoot by pulling the trigger.\r\nYou might have to do something else first to ready the gun though.\r\nMake sure if your gun has a safety it is disengaged.\r\nThis is done by clicking the B button. You should hear a click.\r\nAlso make sure you've got a round chambered!\r\nVisit the Sample Platter scene for an Intro to common gun controls.\r=几乎所有枪支都是通过扣动扳机来射击的。\r\n不过，你可能必须先做些其他事情来准备好枪支。\r\n如果你的枪支有保险装置，确保保险装置已解除。\r\n这可以通过按下B按钮来完成。你应该会听到咔嗒声。\r\n同时确保你已经装好子弹！\r\n访问“样本拼盘”场景，了解常见枪支控制的介绍。\r
Turn your controller around on an empty hand.\r\n\nThe WRIST MENU should appear.\r\n\nPoint at the 'Options Panel' button with your other controller and click.\r\n\nThis will spawn the Options Panel into your hand.\r=将空手的控制器转动。\r\n\n腕上菜单应该会出现。\r\n\n使用另一个控制器指向“选项面板”按钮并单击。\r\n\n这将在你的手中生成选项面板。\r

The Original given new life, "Classic" is a rework of the very first Take & Hold prototype.\n\nIt is entirely indoors and features engagements almost entirely within 50m, with most occuring within 15-25m. The Holiday Winter Wasteland rebuilt for Take & Hold Action!\n\nMassive level with 32 different Holds (use the Hold Order Seed Select to the left to play a consistent sequence of them) Long range engagements, wide open space, extra sentry patrols. You Have a (hard to find) Windows 11 Setting Wrong\nAnd It Will Make H3 Run Like Garbage!\nYou NEED to enable Optimizations for windowed games in Windows 11\n\nThe Button Below will change this setting and close H3 (it needs to be opened again after)\nIf somehow this DOESN'T fix it, you need to go enable the setting yourself.\nIt is Found in Start -> Settings -> System -> Display -> \nGraphics -> Change Default Graphics Settings\nSelect the Setting under Optimizations for windows games to turn it ON.\n\nThen Run H3 Again.=你有个（很难找到的）Windows 11的设置有误\n这将导致H3运行异常！\n你需要在 Windows 11中启用“窗口化游戏优化”\n\n下面的按钮将更改此设置并关闭H3（之后需要手动再次打开游戏）\n如果此操作无法解决问题，你需要自行启用该设置。\n它位于“开始”->“设置”->“系统”->“屏幕”->\n“显示卡”->“更改默认图形设置”\n选择“窗口化游戏优化”将其启用。\n\n然后再次运行 H3。

It looks like your controllers are stuck in the ground! \n\nDo you still need to turn them on?\n\nIf you've turned them on, SteamVR can see them, and they're still down there,\nsomething is broken!\n\nThe most common causes of this are:\n\n- You installed VR Perf Kit (this breaks H3, you need to remove it)\n- You have old/broken mods causing init failure (plz fix them)\n- H3 install is corrupted (try reinstalling it)\n- Oculus runtime / SteamVR are borked (try reinstalling those?)\n\nIf NONE of this fixes your problem, make a post in the Steam Forum\nBug Reports section of the H3 Steam Community and we'll help ya out!=看起来你的控制器卡在地上了！\n\n你是否开启了它们的电源？\n\n如果你已经打开它们，且在SteamVR可以看到它们，但它们仍然卡在地里，\n一定有什么地方坏了！\n\n最常见的原因是：\n\n- 你安装了VRPerfKit（这会破坏H3，你需要将其移除）\n- 你安装了旧的/损坏的模组导致初始化失败（请修复它们）\n- 游戏文件已损坏（尝试重新安装）\n- Oculus运行时/SteamVR已损坏（尝试重新安装它们？）\n\n如果这些都无法解决你的问题，请在H3 Steam社区的Steam论坛\nBug报告部分发帖，我们会帮助你！

REMEMBER where obstacles in your physical space are \nlike TVs, walls, and family members\n\nThrow UNDERHAND and make sure to follow \nthrough for best throw behavior\n\nRelease GRENADE SPOONS (when relevant) to start fuse ticking before you throw\n\nIf you have an INSIDEOUT Tracked HMD, keep your hand VISIBLE to your HMD\n\nIf throws fail or come back at you, release your grip \nEARLIER in your throw\n\nClose targets can be hit with strong OVERHAND throws\n\nDifferent GRENADES are better for different targets. \nRead their stats on the GAME PANEL \nand EXPERIMENT with them!=记住你物理空间中的障碍物在哪里，\n例如电视、墙壁和家庭成员 \n\n用下手投掷并确保遵循\n以获得最佳投掷行为\n\n在投掷前释放手榴弹勺（如适用）以启动引信计时\n\n如果你有一个内向外追踪的头显，请保持你的手在头显可见范围内\n\n如果投掷失败或反弹到你身上，请在投掷时提前松手\n\n近距离目标可以通过强力的上手投掷击中\n\n不同的手榴弹适合不同的目标。\n在游戏面板上阅读它们的统计数据\n并尝试使用它们！
BOOMSKEE TIPS=BOOMSKEE 小贴士
Player starts with 3 GRENADES to throw\n\nPick a grenade up, remove the PIN or CAP with your other hand\n\nThrow the GRENADE along the ramp to launch it into the playfield\n\nContinue throwing GRENADES until none remain\n\nBlow up TROPHIES for HUGE points\n\nBlow up VEHICLES & TROPHIES for extra GRENADES\n\nBlow up BUILDINGS to respawn VEHICLES\n\nBlow up EVERYTHING!!!\n\n=玩家一开始有3颗手榴弹可供投掷\n\n拿起一颗手榴弹，用另一只手拔掉保险销或盖子\n\n沿着斜坡投掷手榴弹，将其扔到游戏场上\n\n继续投掷手榴弹，直到没有剩余\n\n炸毁奖杯可获得巨额积分\n\n炸毁车辆和奖杯可获得额外的手榴弹\n\n炸毁建筑物可重生车辆\n\n炸毁一切！！！\n\n

Create New SaVe=创建新的存档
Complete each difficulty for an item spawner unlock!\n\nClassic Difficulty : \n5000 Life\nBalanced Movement. \nDuplicating mags/clips/cartridges from your quick-belt is disabled!!! \nHold onto empty mags / clips / speedloaders and Use reloadamatics to refill them! \nCrafting supplies (in stomach) persists between runs\n\nArcade Difficulty :\n10000 Life\nNo Movement Restrictions.\nItem spawner\nBetter Starting Equipment +\nAmmo can be duplicated out of your quickbelt (hover empty hand over item in quickbelt and click the thumbpad/joystick to 'spawn lock' it).\n\nHardcore Difficulty:\n2500 Life\nBalanced Movement\nAmmo Duplication Disabled\nCrafting supplies are NOT!!! Persistent\n=完成每个难度即可解锁物品生成器的物品！\n\n经典难度：\n5000 生命值\n平衡移动。\n禁用从快捷腰带复制弹匣/弹夹/弹药筒！！！\n请保留空的弹匣/弹夹/快速装弹器，并使用装填系统进行填充！\n两次游戏之间可持续制作补给（在胃中）\n\n街机难度：\n10000 生命值\n无移动限制。\n物品生成器\n更好的起始装备 +\n弹药可从快捷腰带复制（将空手悬停在快捷腰带中的物品上，然后点击按键/摇杆将其“锁定”）。\n\n极限难度：\n2500 生命值\n平衡移动\n禁用弹药复制\n制作补给不持续！\n
READ THIS FIRST!!!!!!\n\nRogue-like Permadeath: \n\nYOU _WILL_ DIE.\n\nWhen you die or close the game, you lose all of your items, guns, and ammo!!\n\nQuests you complete for NPCS and the rewards NPCs give you are _Permanent_ though. Just swing by their location to get new stuff each run! \n\nAlso, Equipment Cases bought in Stores are always permanent too! Each run you'll get another new semi-random item of the type (ex. Pistol carbine) in that case.\n\n=请先阅读此内容！！！！！！\n\n类Rogue的永久死亡模式：\n\n你_会_死。\n\n当你死亡或关闭游戏时，你将失去所有物品、枪支和弹药！！\n\n不过，你为NPC完成的任务以及NPC给予你的奖励是_永久_的。每次游戏只需前往他们的位置即可获得新物品！\n\n此外，在商店购买的装备箱也是永久的！每次游戏你都会在装备箱中获得另一个新的同类型的半随机物品（例如卡宾枪）。\n\n

Sodalite=Sodalite
The minimum angle (in degrees) from your wrist that you must be looking for the text to render.\nDefault Value: 20=手腕必须看的最低角度（以度为单位），以便文本渲染。\n默认值: 20
ViewAngle=视野角度
Whether or not the text should pitch up to your head.\nDefault Value: True=文本是否应该向上倾斜对准你的头。\n默认值: 是
LockPitch=锁定俯仰
Math=数学
The size of the text. Increasing this but decreasing scale will result in a higher-resolution text.\nDefault Value: 30=文字的大小。增加这个但减少比例将导致更高分辨率的文本。\n默认值: 30
FontSize=字体尺寸
The downward vertical offset, relative to the remaining amount text, of the caliber description.\nDefault Value: 3=口径描述相对于剩余数量文本的向下垂直偏移。\n默认值: 3
CaliberOffset=口径偏移
The scale, relative to the canvas, of the caliber subtext.\nDefault Value: 0.5=相对于画布的口径子文本的大小比例。\n默认值: 0.5
CaliberScale=口径比例
The offset, relative to the center of your hand, to the canvas.\nDefault Value: 0.075=相对于手部中心到画布的偏移量。\n默认值：0.075
TotalOffset=总偏移
The scale of the canvas.\nDefault Value: 0.0075=画布的大小比例。\n默认值: 0.0075
TotalScale=总比例
Proportions=比例
Text=文字
Changes the text which says how much ammo you have.\nDefault Value: Text=更改显示你有多少弹药的文字。\n默认值: 文字
DisplayMode=显示模式

For Those Who Love It All\n\nThis Category is designed around completely open equipment selection.\n\nPart of the challenge is figuring out the best equipment combination for a sequence.\n\nExpect all sorts of target types, combinations, variations in range.\n\nAll Sequences Require Reloading.=给那些喜欢所有目标的人\n\n此类别的设计围绕完全开放的装备选择。\n\n找出序列的最佳装备组合是挑战的一部分。\n\n期待各种目标类型、组合、范围的变化。\n\n所有序列都需要重新装填。

There's gonna be a new one each week, so you can experience the satisfaction that comes from laboring in a wholy artificial construct for imaginary currency to gamble for things with artificial scarcity that don't meaningfully exist.\n\nAnyway... Click one of the buttons below to being working! By clicking you acknowledge that you agree to all employment terms as set forth by G-Form 37.2-B, a copy of which can be obtained via carrier pigeon starting Jan 18th, 2062.=老格伦奇本月有一些绝佳的新就业机会！没错，我们推出一系列特别精选的超级独家、令人心碎的工作，只为你！每周都会有一个新的工作，让你体验在完全人造的结构中劳作，赚取虚拟货币，赌一把人为稀缺、毫无意义的东西所带来的满足感。\n\n总之……点击下方按钮开始工作！点击即表示您同意 G-Form 37.2-B 中的所有雇佣条款，该表格的副本可于 2062 年 1 月 18 日起通过信鸽获取。

Greetings!\n\nWelcome to the Portable Item Spawner! We've got a couple usability things to cover super quick on it:\n\n1. This sucker is a pretty complex object. Its display turns off when in a quickbelt, so if you need to use it in a bunch of places, and get stutters while moving, pop it in a slot before moving!\n\n2. Yes, the text is tiny. That's what happens when you cram a 2ish meter display down to something portable :-P But we did this at request, and knowing the modder folk would just do it -anyway- if we didn't. Just know this wasn't reeeeeeeally design for portability.\n\n3. Use the Stylus on the side for spawning objects (from details pane, or Save/Load). Just point it at a spot and click the trigger while holding the Stylus. Similarly you can use the Stylus to scan objects to save by pointing at them and hitting the Scan button.\n\nAll of us here at RUST LTD. hope you have a Wonderful time!=Greetings!\n\nWelcome to the Portable Item 生成器! We've got a couple usability things to cover super quick on it:\n\n1. This sucker is a pretty complex object. Its display turns off when in a quickbelt, so if you need to use it in a bunch of places, and get stutters while moving, pop it in a slot before moving!\n\n2. Yes, the text is tiny. That's what happens when you cram a 2ish meter display down to something portable :-P But we did this at request, and knowing the modder folk would just do it -anyway- if we didn't. Just know this wasn't reeeeeeeally design for portability.\n\n3. Use the Stylus on the side for spawning objects (from details pane, or 保存/加载). Just point it at a spot and click the trigger while holding the Stylus. Similarly you can use the Stylus to scan objects to save by pointing at them and hitting the Scan button.\n\nAll of us here at RUST LTD. hope you have a Wonderful time!

NAVIGATION=导航
I know some of you folk are just here for new toys, wanna just have a chill time, or have a situation that makes long-range engagement unpleasantly difficult or impossible. So we added more opportunities to heal, as well as turning off Damage. \nYou can change this at any time :-).\n\nTo Heal:\n- Use One Of The Bunker Teleporters (Full Heal)\n- Eat a Security Card! (10/25/50% Heal)\n\nStandard Difficulty:\n5000 Health. Take Damage As Normal.\n\nJust Gimme Gifts Difficulty: \nYou don't take damage.=我知道你们中的一些人来这里只是为了玩新玩具，想放松一下，或者遇到远程战斗难以进行或无法进行的情况。所以我们增加了更多治疗机会，并关闭了伤害。\n您可以随时更改此设置 :-)。\n\n治疗方式：\n- 使用其中一个地堡传送器（完全治疗）\n- 吃一张安全卡！（10/25/50% 治疗）\n\n标准难度：\n5000 生命值。正常受到伤害。\n\n“给我礼物就好”难度：\n您不会受到伤害。

To Reset Winter Wasteland:\nEat The Glowing Red Hot Dog\nWARNING: THIS WILL ERASE PROGRESS IN THIS SCENE BACK TO THE BEGINNING!!=重置寒冬废土：\b吃发光的红色热狗\警告：这将抹去此场景中的进度，回到开始处！！
GREETINGS! Welcome to the Meatmas 2020 Adventure: Winter Wasteland!\n\nThis scene is a sort of... living scene/gamemode. If you're on the Meatmas2020 beta branch on Steam, this will update EVERY DAY at 12:05am Pacific Time\n\nYou should expect New Content, New Enemies, New Messages, Adjustments and Bug Fixes throughout the month, as well as new Areas of the Map to open up.\n\nMake sure to check back each day, hunt for another bunker, shoot some JUNKBOTS, and sift through the remnants of the final days of North Pole!\n\n- NOTE: Your progress in opening Bunkers, SComm Towers and Messages AutoSaves. Weapons you find are NOT saved, but the checkpoints you find them out regenerate new random weapons every time this scene is reloaded. If you die, you will respawn here or at the last teleporter you used.\n\n- PLEASE DO NOT POST SPOILERS TO THE SUBREDDIT OR STEAM FORUM!!!\n=问候！欢迎来到 2020 年圣诞肉节大冒险：寒冬废土！\n\n这个场景应该算是……动态场景/游戏模式。如果你在 Steam 上选择了Meatmas2020测试版渠道，它将在太平洋时间每天凌晨 12:05 更新。\n\n你将在本月内看到新内容、新敌人、新消息、调整和错误修复，以及地图上新的开放区域。\n\n请务必每天回来查看，寻找新的碉堡，射击一些垃圾机器人，并仔细查看北极最后几天的遗迹！\n\n- 注意：你打开碉堡、通信塔和消息的进度会自动保存。你找到的武器不会被保存，但每次重新加载此场景时，你在检查点找到的武器都会随机生成新的武器。如果你死了，你会在这里或你上次使用的传送器处重生。\n\n- 请不要在红迪子区或 STEAM 论坛上发布剧透！！！\n

Meat Grinder=绞肉机
Brave the Meat Grinder, a survival horror experience with procedurally generated challenges and equipment. Can you find the Meat within the Maze and grind it before your 30 minutes runs out? Make sure the inhabitants of the maze don't grind you first!=勇敢面对“绞肉机”，一个带有程序生成的挑战和装备的生存恐怖玩法。你能在30分钟内找到迷宫里的肉并将其绞碎吗？确保迷宫里的生物不会先把你绞碎！
